{"tid":1463200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"犬隻已滲入各手足身邊，一定要知點樣擊退單身犬","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:32:16.000Z","uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d920a0855f927264bdd28f6acc402b3a3142ac","tid":1463200,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UwfEyUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUwfEyUM.jpg&h=d1e06ae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該各位，保護自己，一定每一秒都戴返個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n我明白個手足驚誤會錯人，<br />\n當你發現懷疑狗隻，唔想大叫，<br />\n只要同你身邊既手足，啤實佢，望住佢做仼何野<br />\n啤足佢兩三個字，<br />\n細細聲同其他人講有狗。<br />\n<br />\n佢就自己閃水。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38f1841559cf25391b62108e804c7c8471eb656","tid":1463200,"uid":58803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"!!!!!我頭先都在場，雖然唔係企呢條友隔離，但都feel 到佢勁鬼<br />\n嗌口號大大聲，但d beat 錯撚哂"},{"pid":"15e905f06832a3bffd6400f5648a849d51871963","tid":1463200,"uid":61242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:32:16.000Z","msg":"各位唔好成日低頭望電話，<br />\n我同朋友見到佢鏡頭對出咗好耐，擺明錄影緊人樣。<br />\n所以無勇氣屌柒人，又怕俾人搞分化，<br />\n一定要幾條友近距離望緊佢。<br />\n佢就會走。"}]}